      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Slow Cooker Welsh Lamb Hotpot. A British home-cook's dish, the kind of recipe families adjust across generations. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "It runs in the slow cooker so the work is at the start of the day and the dinner cooks itself.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
